quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  30,6,"WaAAda Allahi la yukhlifu AllahuwaAAdahu walakinna akthara annasi layaAAlamoon"
  30,7,"YaAAlamoona thahiranmina alhayati addunya wahum AAanial-akhirati hum ghafiloon"
  30,8,"Awa lam yatafakkaroo fee anfusihim makhalaqa Allahu assamawati wal-ardawama baynahuma illa bilhaqqiwaajalin musamman wa-inna katheeran mina annasibiliqa-i rabbihim lakafiroon"
  30,9,"Awa lam yaseeroo fee al-ardi fayanthurookayfa kana AAaqibatu allatheena min qablihimkanoo ashadda minhum quwwatan waatharoo al-ardawaAAamarooha akthara mimma AAamarooha wajaat-humrusuluhum bilbayyinati fama kana Allahuliyathlimahum walakin kanoo anfusahumyathlimoon"
  30,10,"Thumma kana AAaqibata allatheenaasaoo assoo-a an kaththaboo bi-ayatiAllahi wakanoo biha yastahzi-oon"
  30,11,"Allahu yabdao alkhalqa thummayuAAeeduhu thumma ilayhi turjaAAoon"
  30,12,"Wayawma taqoomu assaAAatuyublisu almujrimoon"
  30,13,"Walam yakun lahum min shuraka-ihimshufaAAao wakanoo bishuraka-ihim kafireen"
  30,14,"Wayawma taqoomu assaAAatuyawma-ithin yatafarraqoon"
  30,15,"Faamma allatheena amanoowaAAamiloo assalihati fahum fee rawdatinyuhbaroon"
